  "body": "**Steps to reproduce:**\r\n1. Go to any chat as User_A and User_B (for both users chat should be opened in this step)\r\n2. Send the message\r\n3. Pin the message\r\n4. Reply to the message\r\n5. Check the message as User_B\r\n\r\n**Actual  result:**\r\nThe message is not updated in the following places:\r\n- Pinned banner\r\n- Quote\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/220896885-60d0f843-6140-4429-a673-d2b014ec7dda.png)\r\n\r\n- Pinned in the system message\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/220897005-6659456c-3ce7-415b-8421-5e9ff64cae8f.png)\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/220895944-db76c68a-0fff-4328-abdf-8e2728a1ee78.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected result:**\r\nThe message is updated in the following places:\r\n- Pinned banner\r\n- Quote\r\n- Pinned in the system message\r\n\r\n**Additional info:**\r\nThe messages are updated only after the chat is reopened\r\n\r\n**ENV:** Nightly 23 Feb 2023",
